s/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n亦有傳媒拍下短片，有警員在片中稱留守示威者「好垃圾」、「無腦」，又稱對方只能猶如基層、拾荒者等吃「冰冰冷冷的生命麵包」，但他們下班後可以到深圳吃海底撈，又能喝冰凍啤酒。&quot;"},{"pid":"b227be3f7fa2e4ed6249aefce897a13c812b67f2","tid":2372960,"uid":225192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T06:24:32.000Z","msg":"社會寄生蟲警曱仔？"},{"pid":"b06592fdc621abfe499e6f0231be30dce4c49de7","tid":2372960,"uid":8880,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"94b310a6ca3beb86ef10ca75e0e3cb9a6b186e5c","tid":2372960,"uid":37577,"like":162,"dislike":2,"score":160,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T06:06:31.000Z","msg":"//潘官稱：「你地唔好以為法官活係象牙之塔先得架，『毅進仔』正正係恥笑警員低學歷囉」//<br />\n而家咪活緊係象牙塔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋毅進仔又真係平均警員學歷水平<br />\n唔通大學牛又係恥笑緊佢大學生？？定係個官自己有一個先入為主『毅進』係=低學歷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁既話係個官有問題多過個字眼有問題Bo<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T06:26:58.000Z","msg":"象牙塔（Ivory tower），法語 la tour d'ivoire的翻譯，指的是「脫離現實生活的大學等學術機構」，其後引申為「脫離現實生活的學術理論」。<br />\n<br />\n象牙塔不嬲用嚟講學者<br />\n呢個法官以為自己係學者? 唔係學者 唔搞學術 連活係象牙塔嘅資格都冇<br />\n呢個法官連字都唔識用"},{"pid":"0ac1eb982fa26212f30e3b2898b46d3c044e08a6","tid":2372960,"uid":34811,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T06:27:05.000Z","msg":"咁黑警鬧我死曱甴又點計？<br />\n係咪唔叫正當執行職務？"},{"pid":"6a7546fe8a876a1b177ddcf700e4469663ca0195","tid":2372960,"uid":65604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T06:28:08.000Z","msg":"法官認證<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3fd41820a1374f2381458049898c068dea4c728","tid":2372960,"uid":340189,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T06:28:15.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>毅進仔好醜咩？<br />\n醜咁點解政府又推呢個計劃？</strong